487
00:33:21,274 --> 00:33:24,149
Tregoni besim ndaj tyre dhe do te funksionoje,

488
00:33:24,566 --> 00:33:25,900
menjehere do te funksionojne.

489
00:33:26,316 --> 00:33:27,566
Sic Me tregoi Guido qe  

