00:33:27,942 --> 00:33:30,692
"Nene, ata thane qe do te kete shi te dendur

491
00:33:31,191 --> 00:33:32,858
per keto dy dite."

492
00:33:33,274 --> 00:33:37,358
I them, "Mire. Mos u merzit." Ku eshte shiu?

493
00:33:38,608 --> 00:33:41,441
Eshte zhdukur.

494
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:47,441
Ju mund te kontrolloni gjithcka nese besimi eshte nen kontroll.

495
00:33:50,066 --> 00:33:54,274
Dhe kur flasim per besim, e dini,

496
00:33:55,108 --> 00:34:00,566
eshte sfida ndaj kesaj Fuqi gjithe-perhapese,

497
00:34:01,692 --> 00:34:06,400
qe organizon, qe din gjithcka.

498
00:34:06,942 --> 00:34:09,024
qe eshte kaq inteligjinte, efikase

499
00:34:09,441 --> 00:34:10,982
"mbi te gjitha, ajo ju do."

500
00:34:11,358 --> 00:34:14,441
Dhe atehere ju tregon besim.

501
00:34:15,983 --> 00:34:23,108
Ringjallja ne Sahaja Yoga eshte qe besimi juaj eshte solid.

502
00:34:24,358 --> 00:34:29,066
Kete duhet te arrini: besim solid.

503
00:34:29,692 --> 00:34:30,983
Me pas ata nuk ndihen keq,

504
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:34,108
supozoni Une mund te mos i takoj ata,supozoni une mund te them, 

505
00:34:34,483 --> 00:34:36,983
"Mire, eja. Shiko, kete here mund te mos jem ketu."

506
00:34:37,358 --> 00:34:40,441
Nuk ka rendesi, shikoni, edhe nese Nena ju takon ose jo,

507
00:34:40,858 --> 00:34:43,358
nese kjo gje ndodh ose jo.

508
00:34:43,858 --> 00:34:47,775
Cdo gje eshte per te miren tone, per mireqenien tone.

509
00:34:48,233 --> 00:34:49,441
Supozojme ju keni humbur rrugen,

510
00:34:49,817 --> 00:34:53,108
e dini qe kjo duhet te jete rruga.

511
00:34:53,942 --> 00:34:57,650
Nese do te shihni jeten e Krishtit,

512
00:34:58,024 --> 00:34:59,566
Ai ishte per tu kryqezuar.

513
00:34:59,982 --> 00:35:01,400
Ai duhej te mbante kryqin,

514
00:35:01,858 --> 00:35:05,358
Ai duhej te bente gjithe keto gjera "cdo gje eshte ne rregull," sidoqofte.

515
00:35:05,858 --> 00:35:07,775
"Eshte fatkeq. Une do ta bej kete."

516
00:35:08,108 --> 00:35:10,650
Ai kurre nuk u ankua, nuk u qa,

517
00:35:11,066 --> 00:35:15,024
Ai nuk deshi t'i ndante problemet e Tij me askend.

518
00:35:15,566 --> 00:35:18,566
Por ky besim ne Te i dha Atij

519
00:35:18,858 --> 00:35:24,066
forca aq te medha.

520
00:35:25,483 --> 00:35:27,191
Ai mund te kish bere gjithcka.

521
00:35:27,608 --> 00:35:29,692
Ai mund t'i kishte vrare gjithe ata njerez

522
00:35:29,983 --> 00:35:33,608
qe ishin duke u perpjekjur ta perndiqnin ate, kollaj "C'dem ka?

