00:35:33,982 --> 00:35:35,942
Vetem nje shikim mund t'i vriste ata.

524
00:35:36,358 --> 00:35:39,400
Por jo, Ai e dinte Ai duhet ta kalonte gjithe kete,

525
00:35:39,733 --> 00:35:40,942
Ai e kaloi ate.

526
00:35:41,274 --> 00:35:44,775
Se fundmi, Ai eshte ai qe eshte fitimtari,

527
00:35:45,149 --> 00:35:47,983
Ai eshte ai qe fitoi gjithcka.

528
00:35:48,692 --> 00:35:50,525
Ne te njejten menyre, nje Sahaja yogi

529
00:35:50,900 --> 00:35:52,733
duhet te shohe jeten e tij.

530
00:35:53,149 --> 00:35:59,525
Eshte shume e shtrenjte, jeta, eshte shume e shtrenjte ne kete bote.

531
00:36:00,441 --> 00:36:04,566
Keto dite, sa Sahaja Yogis ka?

532
00:36:05,066 --> 00:36:06,982
Ne procesin zhvillues (evoluiv)?

533
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:10,942
sa do te behen Sahaja yogis, Une s'mund ta them.

534
00:36:11,525 --> 00:36:17,775
Se pari shihni boten, me pas do filloni te ndjeni qe

535
00:36:18,274 --> 00:36:20,817
shume prej saj po shkaterrohet ose po mbaron,

536
00:36:21,233 --> 00:36:23,983
shumica e njererzve nuk do te jene me.

537
00:36:24,441 --> 00:36:25,900
Jo se ne s'jemi te gatshem,

538
00:36:26,316 --> 00:36:31,982
por sepse ata nuk jane te destinuar

539
00:36:32,566 --> 00:36:34,233
te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga,

540
00:36:34,566 --> 00:36:36,858
s'eshte e thene te vijne ne Sahaja Yoga.

541
00:36:37,233 --> 00:36:38,775
Pra, ju jeni kaq fatlume

542
00:36:39,149 --> 00:36:43,024
qe keni arritur realizimin tuaj, rilindjen tuaj.

543
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:46,400
Por tani keni besim ne kete rilindjen tuajen,

544
00:36:46,817 --> 00:36:51,233
ne rilindjen tuaj qe eshte qenia juaj tani.

545
00:36:51,733 --> 00:36:54,775
Dhe me kete ju do te dini sa te cmuar

546
00:36:55,149 --> 00:36:57,942
jeni ju per kete bote,

547
00:36:58,316 --> 00:37:00,441
dhe ajo qe ju duhet te beni s'eshte

548
00:37:00,775 --> 00:37:03,525
te mendoni per fitimin material, fizik

549
00:37:03,982 --> 00:37:09,233
apo fitime emocionale, por fitime shpirterore.

550
00:37:10,108 --> 00:37:14,650
Cfare kemi bere per spiritualitetin, tonin dhe te tjereve?

551
00:37:15,149 --> 00:37:17,191
Kjo eshte e vetmja gje qe duhet te mendoni,

552
00:37:17,566 --> 00:37:19,817
dhe do te habiteni, cdo gje eshte organizuar,

553
00:37:20,191 --> 00:37:21,274
gjithcka funksionon.

554
00:37:21,775 --> 00:37:25,441
cdo gje ne kohen e vet tregon rezultatet e saja.

555
00:37:27,608 --> 00:37:31,400
Tani une jam e sigurte te pakten tetedhjete perqind prej jush

556
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:36,942
besojne ne ate qe po them "themi mbase, nentedhjete perqind."

557
00:37:39,983 --> 00:37:45,900
Por mund te kete rreth dhjete perqind qe ende mendojne qe

558
00:37:46,233 --> 00:37:47,733
"Ne rregull, Nena thote keshtu.

559
00:37:48,066 --> 00:37:51,274
Por pse ndodhi me pas, pse ndodhi kjo?"

560
00:37:51,858 --> 00:37:53,525
Si dje kisha nje gazetar,

561
00:37:53,983 --> 00:37:56,942
person mjaft i njohur, ai tha, "Une s'mund te besoj ne Zot."

562
00:37:57,316 --> 00:37:58,316
E pyes, "Pse?"

563
00:37:58,650 --> 00:38:02,983
"Sepse si mund te kete kaq shume mjerim ne kete bote?

564
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,358
Si mund te kete nje femije te verber,

565
00:38:05,650 --> 00:38:08,149
si mundet kjo e si mundet ajo?"

566
00:38:08,608 --> 00:38:11,066
Pastaj filloi te me jepte Mua raste. "Ne rregull tani,"

567
00:38:11,358 --> 00:38:13,191
I them, "Me ke treguar gjithcka?"
"Po".

568
00:38:13,608 --> 00:38:16,900
I them, "Tani, supozojme te themi qe

569
00:38:17,149 --> 00:38:22,191
ju jeni ulur ne mbreterine (fushen) e kongresit te qeverise,

570
00:38:22,566 --> 00:38:27,066
apo qeveria juaj e Andreottit apo sidoqe e quani.

571
00:38:28,566 --> 00:38:31,900
Pra situata eshte e sqarueshme;

572
00:38:32,316 --> 00:38:36,775
ju nuk keni hyre ende ne mbreterine (fushen) e Zotit.

573
00:38:37,483 --> 00:38:41,233
Nese shkoni ne ate gjendje, dhe nese e arrini ate

574
00:38:41,650 --> 00:38:43,525
dhe nese ju stabilizoheni, atehere Me thoni,

575
00:38:43,983 --> 00:38:47,942
a keni ndonje problem? Asnje."

576
00:38:50,775 --> 00:38:52,983
Them, "Pse shikoni anen negative?

577
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:57,191
Tani nese ju thoni qe ka nje rruge dalje

578
00:38:57,650 --> 00:39:00,650
dhe qe ka nje zgjidhje,

579
00:39:01,066 --> 00:39:04,108
dhe qe mund te vije nje kohe

580
00:39:04,441 --> 00:39:07,358
kur kjo race e Sahaja Yogis nuk do te kete semundje,

581
00:39:07,775 --> 00:39:11,149
jo shqetesime, asgje, asnje problem;

582
00:39:12,982 --> 00:39:14,650
pse nuk e shikoni kete?

583
00:39:15,024 --> 00:39:18,733
Pse doni te shihni nje djale qe eshte i verber?

584
00:39:20,024 --> 00:39:23,982
Por s'shihni qe i verberi behet mire?"

585
00:39:25,650 --> 00:39:27,817
Por kete lloj sjelljeje negative

586
00:39:28,191 --> 00:39:30,316
mund ta kene edhe Sahaja yogis.

587
00:39:30,775 --> 00:39:33,024
I kam pare: dikush eshte i semure,

588
00:39:33,483 --> 00:39:35,982
ata do thone, "Nene, ai eshte semure, Duhet ta sjelle ate tek Ty.

589
00:39:36,274 --> 00:39:39,525
Duhet ti shikoni ata. "S'eshte nevoja fare."

590
00:39:40,066 --> 00:39:44,525
Ju mund te sheroni, besimi juaj mund te sheroje.

591
00:39:45,024 --> 00:39:47,858
E dini dikush kishte xhaxhain semure,

592
00:39:48,233 --> 00:39:49,483
e nuk ishte nje Sahaja Yogi.

593
00:39:49,982 --> 00:39:53,608
Ai shkoi ta vizitonte ate, dhe gruaja e tij i thote qe

594
00:39:53,982 --> 00:39:56,233
"Ti je i afte t'i lutesh Nenes.

595
00:39:56,733 --> 00:40:01,149
Pse nuk i thua Asaj te me beje mire burrin?"

596
00:40:01,566 --> 00:40:04,358
Ai ishte nje i semure me kancer ne shtratin e vdekjes.

597
00:40:04,817 --> 00:40:07,566
Ai tha, "Ne rregull." Ai vetem u perul dhe u lut,

598
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:10,066
"Nene, te lutem sheroje xhaxhain tim."

599
00:40:10,483 --> 00:40:11,942
Diten trete ai doli nga spitali,

600
00:40:12,191 --> 00:40:14,400
dhe tani eshte duke bredhur ne te gjithe boten.

601
00:40:14,817 --> 00:40:18,400
Megjithese ai s'ishte nje Sahaja yogi, perseri funksionoi.

602
00:40:18,817 --> 00:40:21,024
sepse tani nje Sahaja jogi po thote qe,

603
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:23,692
hyjnite duhet ta zgjidhin.

604
00:40:24,149 --> 00:40:27,316
Nese ai nuk eshte nje Sahaja yogi, nuk ka rendesi.

605
00:40:27,858 --> 00:40:30,692
Jane hyjnite qe jane me te.

606
00:40:34,650 --> 00:40:41,108
Dhe ky duhet ta besoje kete vete, plotesisht,

607
00:40:41,900 --> 00:40:47,900
qe nese keto fuqi jane me ne, pse mos t'i perdorim ato?

608
00:40:48,650 --> 00:40:52,149
Pse te mos e zhvillojme kete besim te plote

609
00:40:52,650 --> 00:40:54,525
qe ne jemi tani Sahaja yogis,

610
00:40:54,942 --> 00:40:57,900
ne jemi ne Mbreterine e Zotit,

611
00:40:58,400 --> 00:41:02,650
dhe qe kjo Fuqi do te kujdeset per ne?

612
00:41:03,191 --> 00:41:05,775
Pastaj nuk do te kemi zgjedhje,

613
00:41:06,233 --> 00:41:12,108
nuk do te kemi hezitime.

614
00:41:12,983 --> 00:41:16,525
Nuk do e vrasim mendjen, nese duhet te shkojme, te themi,

615
00:41:16,942 --> 00:41:19,400
ne Singapor ose duhet te shkojme ne Afrike

616
00:41:19,817 --> 00:41:21,982
apo te shkojme kudo "Edhe cfare?

617
00:41:22,441 --> 00:41:25,650
Ne jemi ende ne Mbreterine e Zotit kudo qe te shkojme,

618
00:41:26,024 --> 00:41:28,650
eshte krejtesisht ne rregull.

619
00:41:29,191 --> 00:41:31,566
Dhe asnje lloj shqetesimi.

620
00:41:31,983 --> 00:41:34,525
Ne jemi skllever te shume gjerave, te hapave tone,

621
00:41:34,858 --> 00:41:37,274
ne jemi skllever te kushtezimeve, e gjerave te tilla.

622
00:41:37,650 --> 00:41:39,400
Cdo gje kalon.

623
00:41:39,817 --> 00:41:41,108
S'ka rendesi.

624
00:41:41,525 --> 00:41:44,400
Cfare ka rendesi? Asgje s'eshte e rendesishme.

625
00:41:44,858 --> 00:41:48,650
Per sa kohe ti je me veten tende, cdo gje eshte ne rregull.

626
00:41:49,108 --> 00:41:50,066
Sic Me thone njerezit,

627
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,775
"Nene, Ju udhetoni kaq shume. Si e beni ju kete?"

628
00:41:52,108 --> 00:41:54,900
U them, "Une nuk udhetoj asnjehere. Meqe jam e ulur ketu ne karrige,

629
00:41:55,149 --> 00:41:57,733
Une jam e ulur aty ne karrige, kjo eshte e gjitha;

630
00:41:58,191 --> 00:41:59,316
vetem karrigia ndryshon.

631
00:41:59,733 --> 00:42:01,983
Kurre nuk mendoj se po udhetoj. E ulur per bukuri,

632
00:42:02,358 --> 00:42:07,108
vendosur ne vendin Tim, Une jam shume mire, pra s'jam e lodhur."

633
00:42:08,566 --> 00:42:14,692
Pra kur keni besimin e plote ne veten tuaj,

634
00:42:15,233 --> 00:42:17,775
atehere nuk e vrisni mendjen.

635
00:42:18,233 --> 00:42:20,692
Shume njerez do duan te dijne se nese

636
00:42:21,024 --> 00:42:23,441
"Une shkoj atje" do te kete apo nuk do te kete banjo,

637
00:42:23,817 --> 00:42:28,358
ose do te kete vend per te fjetur ose jo?" Asgje.

638
00:42:30,858 --> 00:42:33,274
Ju po shikoni per komfortin e shpirtit tuaj.

639
00:42:33,692 --> 00:42:37,316
Nese behet me se miri, perndryshe ju mund te flini kudo.

640
00:42:37,817 --> 00:42:40,692
Asgje nuk ju lidh,

641
00:42:41,149 --> 00:42:42,900
asgje nuk ju shemb,

642
00:42:43,233 --> 00:42:47,066
asnje zakon nuk ju kthehet;

643
00:42:49,066 --> 00:42:54,358
sepse besimi do ju pastroje teresisht,

644
00:42:54,942 --> 00:42:57,983
